<PB REF="101">
<P><FIGURE>
<P>F<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter">ller Pinxit ad Alt: Coll: Magd: Oxon: Delin Mburg. &s;culpt. Univ. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 word"></P>
</FIGURE></P>
